title: clear_selected_folders()
brief: Clear all selected folders.
seealso: add_selected_folder, toggle_selected_folder, selected_folders, on_folder_selection, set_selected_folder
version: 0.07
----

<p><span class="tt">lumail</span> allows you to select multiple folders to open at the same time.</p>
<p>The <span class="tt">clear_selected_folders()</span> function allows you to unselect all currently selected folders.</p>
